title: Electric president
description:
The self-titled Electric President took us about 8 months to track, and it was recorded in Alex&#039;s bedroom and my toolshed. The initial concept behind the record was to see what happens when computers were integrated into the song writing process. Later on, other concepts were added (the songs all being about various "futures", and other silly stuff like that), but that was where it all began.

Wonderful album
